{"tid":270257,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"地盤佬絕對係人生贏家","createTime":"2017-06-04T08:19:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-07T00:32:42.000Z","uid":55369,"like":3,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9b82889023b26f4e5ea889acceb11bd3448b677f","tid":270257,"uid":55369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T08:19:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">以一個case 去解釋我既講法 睇完再駁我</span><br />\n首先依家假設你啱啱DSE 完18歲<br />\n去上完綠卡堂同搵左張證<br />\n<br />\n一入行係初工 人工已經650~750 一日<br />\n當平均700 你一星期休一日<br />\n700*26=<span style=\"color: red;\">18200</span><br />\n(香港月入中位數18000)<br />\n<br />\n返工一餐lunch <br />\n一餐下午茶<br />\n入老細數，冇支出<br />\n<br />\n返工：<br />\n極端例如 上水到海洋公園開工<br />\n一日來回<span style=\"color: red;\">約40</span><br />\n<br />\n當你自己食早餐晚餐<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">約40+50</span><br />\n<br />\n你休息果幾日多數會約fd 玩/shopping<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">一個月洗2000</span><br />\n<br />\n(700-40-90)*26-2000=<span style=\"color: red;\">12820純收入（儲蓄）</span><br />\n<br />\n多數2 3個月就已經由初工升中工<br />\n(人工由700升到<span style=\"color: red;\">900</span>)<br />\n<br />\n(900-40-90)*26-3000=<span style=\"color: red;\">17020(儲蓄）</span>)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港月入平均數2萬2</span></span><br />\n<br />\n3年左右升上大工<br />\n(由900上<span style=\"color: red;\">1200</span>)<br />\n<br />\n(1200-40-90)*26-5000=<span style=\"color: red;\">22830(儲蓄）</span><br />\n<br />\n由於上左大工後加薪不定 所以唔準啦<br />\n<br />\n由於地盤算係散工 <br />\n所以你甚至可以申請埋綜援<br />\n每個月又有6000額外收入<br />\n又可以神速上公屋<br />\n唔洗比租<br />\n水電煤700一個月啦當<br />\n<br />\n12820*3+17020*33+6000-700=<span style=\"color: red;\">790920</span><br />\n<br />\n一個2房一廳既靚單位700萬<br />\n(7000000-790920)/(22830+5300)<span style=\"color: red;\">=220個月</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">13年就可以上到樓！而你先32歲</span></span><br />\n<br />\n有幾多人做到！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b5a50829807588fbde703b83e85dd5b973f4d21","tid":270257,"uid":120462,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T08:21:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c0f9f4876597b75401d9bc9d1916e458741aa6d0","tid":270257,"uid":55369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T08:22:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搭車坐開d啦屌你老母</blockquote><br />\n駁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d99955be219bc242cf0fb8fb48ec8d2da10160d2","tid":270257,"uid":65825,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T08:29:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>搭車坐開d啦屌你老母</blockquote><br />\n駁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幾好架 搭地鐵企埋去d人雞飛狗走包有位坐"},{"pid":"1907e8c34de16fb15920f6e16bde8bc10ec5c4df","tid":270257,"uid":2746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T08:36:58.000Z","msg":"淨係準時放工已經屌打大部分人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38f154dc4e9e5519a62f32e882b800fe6d655c0d","tid":270257,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T08:39:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"96090dfd728953800c3a98c31287a0ea1798c8d6","tid":270257,"uid":106430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T08:54:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>搭車坐開d啦屌你老母</blockquote><br />\n駁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n神回<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1c2146be1dc44ea3f28c6e8673962dcf0509b37","tid":270257,"uid":99028,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T08:55:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4a1dde0dbc844069cb03e2c