":"<blockquote><blockquote>你覺得13年後仲係700萬？</blockquote><br />\n同埋讀兩年HD ，有朋友讀土木一畢業都有3皮，大電正常都1.8-2.2萬，計你本身廢，要10年先升到工程師，有4-7萬，未計加人工個D，4年就追平，然後一直差距越來越大，最後工程撚完勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我點知咁清楚姐<br />\n前排阿哥返地盤搵快錢<br />\n啱啱返左一日月就黎同我講呢篇野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咪share 下囉"},{"pid":"b1ce40bc366993f85daccf7fc7a080156188d12f","tid":270257,"uid":25221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T10:30:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ea9dbd29d0b558a427170047f6e99c9f6a656aea","tid":270257,"uid":75372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T10:32:20.000Z","msg":"地盤好撚辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57c0f069e67fc06ef31732dbdc12c87e67aa469d","tid":270257,"uid":30468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T10:33:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">以一個case 去解釋我既講法 睇完再駁我</span><br />\n首先依家假設你啱啱DSE 完18歲<br />\n去上完綠卡堂同搵左張證<br />\n<br />\n一入行係初工 人工已經650~750 一日<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">當平均700 你一星期休一日<br />\n700*26=<span style=\"color: red;\">18200</span></span><br />\n(香港月入中位數18000)<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n就算好景都未必日日有工開"},{"pid":"71eea40a3ee744b14a187ce946b55b1604b32ed4","tid":270257,"uid":35644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T13:41:17.000Z","msg":"今日嘅天氣要你做地盤你肯唔肯先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9869ec155cf7271e7125fd59b9629d45abe7bc7","tid":270257,"uid":65144,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T13:51:58.000Z","msg":"一到呢d時間又係老點dse雞年輕人落地盤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n工業意外呢？<br />\n勞損呢？<br />\n做到傷曬又冇學歷，人到中年冇經驗冇學歷又難搵返文職<br />\n<br />\n我以前學過電，學徒制勁低人工，我做左幾個月就冇做<br />\n早兩年有個師兄打黎問我乞幾百蚊食飯<br />\n又有個電死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2ce91c6413ae84788dcbe94c77c5006832d2118","tid":270257,"uid":65144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T13:53:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>地盤好撚辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n工作環境極度惡劣，d廢中坑同事又西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76b49aa80675db291fdb8d2277c0a1c0aed0c4ab","tid":270257,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T13:58:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一到呢d時間又係老點dse雞年輕人落地盤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n工業意外呢？<br />\n勞損呢？<br />\n做到傷曬又冇學歷，人到中年冇經驗冇學歷又難搵返文職<br />\n<br />\n我以前學過電，學徒制勁低人工，我做左幾個月就冇做<br />\n早兩年有個師兄打黎問我乞幾百蚊食飯<br />\n又有個電死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢行真係好危險，識唔少跌死，無左隻手，但係唔會報"},{"pid":"de6780ea10fb794f1493b62d7274452f91fde272","tid":270257,"uid":65144,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T13:59:46.000Z","msg":"講到咁撚好咪叫你家人朋友兄弟姊妹做啦，係度瑞士山區肺介紹d網民做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e099dbf4c754cd8ef9041cf74d50ce6fc1fc8f49","tid":270257,"uid":9210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T14:13:19.000Z","msg":"我做左五年呢行，過過月都平均25日以上<br />\n係搵唔少。<br />\n但都唔估勵人入行吹奏啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}